  m_Name: Scoured Obelisk
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::UnknownMapEventSO
  displayName: The Scoured Obelisk
  description: "A pillar of white marble stands incongruously amidst the gloom, vibrating
    with a high-pitched, cleansing frequency. It is a 'Reset' point a remnant of
    Merlin\u2019s early attempts to keep his reality perfectly sterile. As you place
    your die against the cold stone, the jagged, purple corruption of the Curse begins
    to flake off like dry mud, revealing the smooth, stable mana-surface beneath.
    The static in your head clears, if only for a moment."
  eventArt: {fileID: 0}
